name: Don't listen to the snakes...
description:
Snakes. A representation of treachery, betrayal and traitors

"Beware of what lurks behind the flowers, there is a predator ready to devour. They take advantage of your trust, slowly whispering lies. calming you down until you are paralyzed. They will grow in your head taking over your mind. Deception so powerful that the truth becomes hard to find. So shut your eyes and cover your ears. Watch out for the snake's whisper if it appears.Hold on to the truth that you believe, ignore the snakes and hope that they will leave. Fear for the snake that tells you a lie, for when the time is right the truth may come by".
